er ) ..<br><br>Hand it to them and they will say this will cost you Xg to enchant this item...also do this with all crafted armor too !<br><br>Makes a MAJOR differance ! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/udarkith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Darkith</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Member</span><br>  Posts: 56<br> <font color=#ff0000>(5/10/02 12:18:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://asgarthvanguard.com/images/avcrest.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lvl 13 and a good Magic hammer?</span><hr size=1> I have a 98% quality Shimmering Arcanium Great Hammer.  My weapon damage rating with it equiped is 1587.  My weapon damage rating with my 100% quality Hammer of Black Ice is only 1500.<br><br>High quality crafted weapons ARE the way to go! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br> <p>-----------------------------------<br><b>Darkith - lvl 50 Troll Skald</b><br><a href="http://asgarthvanguard.com"><b>[ Asgarth's Vanguard ]</b></a><br><b>Iseult</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/ugainsward2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gainsward2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#ff0000>(5/10/02 5:55:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lvl 13 and a good Magic hammer?</span><hr size=1> The hammer I had made is only 94% QUALITY. Can it be incr